OL,3,CDrilling Antarctica: What ice can tell
OL,4,Cus about our past and the future
OL,6,FThe oldest ice core ever to be drilled
OL,7,Fhas arrived in the UK for scientists
OL,8,Fto start analysing, as ITV News
OL,9,FScience Correspondent Martin Stew
OL,10,Freports
OL,12,FWords by ITV News Senior Producer,
OL,13,FRhiannon Hopley
OL,15,FIn the freezing temperatures of
OL,16,FAntarctica, the nearly 3km thick ice
OL,17,Fcontains a perfectly preserved record
OL,18,Fof our planet's history.
