OL,3,CDrilling Antarctica: What ice can tell
OL,4,Cus about our past and the future
OL,6,FAs part of an ambitious project to
OL,7,Funlock these secrets, European
OL,8,Fscientists have drilled down into the
OL,9,Fice and extracted a core which is
OL,10,F2.8km long.
OL,12,FThis long core has been pulled out
OL,13,Ffrom the middle of the Antarctic ice
OL,14,Fsheet and scientists think the deepest
OL,15,Fpart could be more than 1.5million
OL,16,Fyears old.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
