OL,3,CDrilling Antarctica: What ice can tell
OL,4,Cus about our past and the future
OL,6,FThe scientists melt the cores and run
OL,7,Fthem through machines, looking for
OL,8,Fthree main things: how much carbon
OL,9,Fdioxide was in the atmosphere at the
OL,10,Ftime, the temperature and any
OL,11,Fimpurities in the ice.
OL,13,FIn the ice core, impurities can show
OL,14,Fwhen there have been volcanic
OL,15,Feruptions or other big historical
OL,16,Fevents, including the atomic bombs
OL,17,Fdropped on Japan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
