OL,3,CDrilling Antarctica: What ice can tell
OL,4,Cus about our past and the future
OL,6,FIt will also provise more evidence for
OL,7,Fhow carbon dioxide levels affect our
OL,8,Fplanet's temperature and conditions as
OL,9,Flooking this far back into the past
OL,10,Fmay just help reveal our future.
